=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Guides_Tour_of_UGens_ex15 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_bright mixed sound, with sine_like oscillator character around 409 Hz, featuring very_slow attack and dynamic envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with steep_rolloff character, and spectrally dense.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: very_slow
  brightness: very_bright
  crest_factor_db: dynamic
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: mixed
  spectral_complexity_mean: dense
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 409.3564
  harmonic_decay_rate: -5.2210
  harmonic_regularity: 0.9918
  pitch_clarity: 24.9258
  inharmonicity: 0.8360
  type: sine_like
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -2.9297
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: Tour of UGens Example 15
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Guides/Tour_of_UGens.html
// Tags: Tour_of_UGens, Guides
// ---
// --- Example 15 ---
{ Saw.ar(XLine.kr(20000,200,6),0.2) }.play;
{ Saw.ar(XLine.kr(100,15000,6),0.2) }.play; // no aliasing
